description:
The Broads get honest about their opinions on "The Men Tell All" aka Luke’s Trial. They chat A LOT about Luke (because that was 95% of the show), major production shockers, WWJPJD?, bloopers, Hannah’s badass podium skills, Bachelor in Paradise, and more!
